    📦 CONTAINER PLATFORM
       • Docker CE with BuildX & Compose
       • Podman & Buildah for OCI containers
       • Tailscale for secure networking
    
    🖥️  MANAGEMENT TOOLS
       • Cockpit web console (port 9090)
       • Libvirt/KVM virtualization
       • System monitoring with PCP
    
